  levelStory: '<color=#00B4FF>Level 7/12</color>


    Oh no, the judges have caught
    on that the other team has been bribed! But they can''t shut down the game while
    it''s live! Instead, a decoy <color=red>red-shirt players</color> have subbed
    in, and they will do the OPPOSITE X and Y coordinates of the signals! So B3 becomes
    A3, and A1 becomes B5, etc.'
